{"tid":1689419,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"誰才是我 都拈花一笑忘記","createTime":"2019-11-02T19:40:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-02T20:35:23.000Z","uid":170867,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"044a0ea166be57ec8d68a85bd2e7b65b1b4105e8","tid":1689419,"uid":170867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T19:40:55.000Z","msg":"「我是誰？ 」<br />\n恐怕是活在痛苦中的人才會思考的一個理性的問題<br />\n弗洛伊德說：「理性是一種防禦」<br />\n可是 誰不曾痛苦過？<br />\n<br />\n「我是誰？」<br />\n多少人窮其一生去尋找答案<br />\n蘇格拉底說：「認識你自己」<br />\n到頭來，幾多人也只是演繹了自己<br />\n<br />\n雖則也是一種存在的哲學<br />\n可這些人卻有否想過<br />\n「我是誰？」這個問題<br />\n真的那麼重要嗎？"},{"pid":"96c76026063e482acb139f14030baeae6badcb20","tid":1689419,"uid":170867,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T19:41:26.000Z","msg":"來讓我唱 櫻吹雪蕩誰在飛<br />\n飛花入泥泥內有花氣<br />\n我見我如無物這個境界與何人說起"},{"pid":"8e73ca126fcb8d59d624fe11cb1c430b73ec4081","tid":1689419,"uid":170867,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T19:41:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"535eacd5c08fdd7d195efcae9aee5648066afbb2","tid":1689419,"uid":170867,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T20:35:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}